stateDiagram-v2
CineQuerySystemStateChart
    
    [*] --> Idle
    
    state Idle
    state Searching
    state ResultsActive
    state NoResults
    state ErrorState
    state MovieDetails
    state Favorites
    
    %% Main flow transitions
    Idle --> Searching : User searches
    Searching --> ResultsActive : Movies found
    Searching --> NoResults : No movies found
    Searching --> ErrorState : API error
    NoResults --> Searching : User retries
    NoResults --> Idle : User clears search
    ErrorState --> Searching : User retries
    ErrorState --> Idle : User dismisses error
    ResultsActive --> Searching : New search
    ResultsActive --> MovieDetails : Click movie
    MovieDetails --> ResultsActive : Close details
    MovieDetails --> Favorites : Navigate to favorites
    
    %% Navigation transitions
    Idle --> Favorites : Navigate to favorites
    ResultsActive --> Favorites : Navigate to favorites
    Favorites --> Idle : Navigate to home
    Favorites --> MovieDetails : Click favorite
    
    %% State notes
    note right of Idle
        Display featured movies
        Show search interface
        Display carousels
        State variables
        movies empty
        loading false
    end note
    
    note right of Searching
        API request in progress
        Show loading indicator
        State variables
        loading true
        movies empty
        API endpoints
        api search
        api ai-search
    end note
    
    note right of ResultsActive
        Display search results
        Show movie grid
        Carousels visible
        State variables
        loading false
        movies populated
    end note
    
    note right of NoResults
        Display no results message
        Carousels still visible
        State variables
        loading false
        movies empty
    end note
    
    note right of ErrorState
        Display error message
        Allow retry
        State variables
        loading false
        error present
    end note
    
    note right of MovieDetails
        Display movie information
        Show where to watch
        Favorites button
        State variables
        selected movie object
        movieData fetched
        API endpoint:
        api movies details by id
    end note
    
    note right of Favorites
        Display favorite movies
        Show recommendations
        State variables
        view favorites
        selected null or movie object
        Data source
        FavoritesContext
        LocalStorage
    end note
